typeProperties.script:
source(output(
		SOURCE_CODE_KEY as string,
		SOURCE_SYSTEM as string,
		TARGET_CODE as string,
		TARGET_DESCRIPTION as string,
		CODE_TYPE as string,
		CODE_TYPE_ID as double,
		CODE2 as string,
		OM_X_REF as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	format: 'parquet') ~> TCrossReference
source(output(
		PK_KEY as string,
		CPT_DESCRIPTION as string,
		CPT_NUMBER as integer,
		INSERTED_BY as string,
		DATE_INSERTED as date
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	format: 'parquet') ~> PreDimAgreementTypeInput
TCrossReference filter(CODE_TYPE_ID == 113) ~> FilterAgreementType113
FilterAgreementType113 aggregate(groupBy(TARGET_DESCRIPTION),
	TARGET_CODE = first(TARGET_CODE)) ~> Deduplicator
Deduplicator select(mapColumn(
		description = TARGET_DESCRIPTION,
		key = TARGET_CODE
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RenameOutputColumn
RenameOutputColumn lookup(ERROR_FUNCTION('') == ERROR_FUNCTION(''),
	multiple: false,
	pickup: 'any',
	broadcast: 'none')~> Lookup1
Lookup1 split(ERROR_FUNCTION(''),
	disjoint: false) ~> ExistingRows@(ExistingRows, NewRows)
PreDimAgreementTypeInput select(mapColumn(
		PK_KEY,
		CPT_DESCRIPTION,
		CPT_NUMBER,
		INSERTED_BY,
		DATE_INSERTED
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> Select1
